91f010","tid":926061,"uid":20284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:15:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/UEFA_Europa_League#Distribution_(from_2021%E2%80%9322_to_2023%E2%80%9324)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FUEFA_Europa_League%23Distribution_%28from_2021%25E2%2580%259322_to_2023%25E2%2580%259324%29&d=E19L6z%2Bp8GfveTtRqWmKGb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8ae11c82\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/UEFA_Europa_League#Distribution_(from_2021%E2%80%9322_to_2023%E2%80%9324)</a><br />\n歐霸2詳細參賽資格<br />\n五大聯賽各一隊<br />\n6-15位兩隊<br />\n52-55位兩隊(列支敦士登及聖馬力諾只有一個席位)<br />\n其他都有三隊<br />\n<br />\n歐霸同歐霸2都會採用相同賽制<br />\n32隊分組賽只有小組首名直入16強<br />\n歐霸小組第2要同歐聯小組第3爭16強"},{"pid":"0559bc69f1f0787dc771fd8194b67fdc6d798d64","tid":926061,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:16:35.000Z","msg":"又多一「飯」賭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6042608cb23a7ec941ea28a1dad48523209173","tid":926061,"uid":131690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:50:15.000Z","msg":"整埋D撚屌聯賽，歐國聯已經on9，仲整多個咩歐霸2，不如整埋南半球聯，北半球聯算撚柒數啦你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18793ac6e22a6cb73ab497c7b4bc9c3b4e07de0f","tid":926061,"uid":9305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:52:19.000Z","msg":"屌咁咪即係圖圖杯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b11ab2a11390140ab3b3f66bf773c8c9a8efaf7","tid":926061,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:55:56.000Z","msg":"曼聯又贏"},{"pid":"895c9d24238530824f6b09664c0a07c328641f16","tid":926061,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T10:57:28.000Z","msg":"以前唔係有個咩陶陶杯咩"}]}